  PLAIN TEXT TASK MANAGEMENT (EXPERIMENTAL)

A little experiment for one milestone to see if text format would be more convenient.

- plain text
- single flat folder
- each task's ID is their short name in kebab-case
- references are in form "./kebab-case"
- all tasks belong to the engine project/repo


  PROS

- Easy conversion of NEXT/TODO task to a tracked one
- Easy editing of tasks


  CONS

- Github issues are pretty
